 <name>GNU FreeDink</name>
 <summary>Humorous top-down adventure &amp; role-playing game</summary>
 <description>
  <p>
   Dink Smallwood is an adventure/role-playing game, similar to
   classic Zelda, made by RTsoft. Besides twisted humour, it includes
   the actual game editor, allowing players to create hundreds of new
   adventures called Dink Modules or D-Mods for short.
  </p>
  <p>
   GNU FreeDink is a new and portable version of the game engine, which
   runs the original game as well as its D-Mods, with close
   compatibility, under multiple platforms.
  </p>
 </description>
